            <p class="font-archivo font-stretch-extra-expanded font-medium text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-tight tracking-tight-1 text-black archivo-variable">
              <span class="italic">Turang</span> is not just a recovered relic, but proof that Indonesia helped shape the very ethos later known as Third Cinema.<sup>1</sup>
            </p>
